N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4822.7 - Effect of revocation

State Regulations

No licensed authorized organization that has had its
identification number or bingo license revoked shall, after 30 days of the
effective date of revocation, rent or allow the use of such organization's
premises for the conduct of bingo. Notes
